{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act33side_level_act33side_03_end","storyGroup":"act33side","storySort":7,"storyDependence":"act33side_level_act33side_03_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"BB-3","storyName":"无声破裂","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"卡兹戴尔城内，不同理念的萨卡兹之间的冲突终于到了不可收拾的地步，特蕾西娅最终决定带着支持自己的人民离开自己的家园。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act33side/level_act33side_03_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act33side_03","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":5,"next":7,"characters":["奥达","萨卡兹王庭军","冷漠的平民","激愤的平民","谨慎的平民","讥讽的平民","“老师”","沉默的佣兵","虚弱的孩子","巴别塔成员","冷淡的王庭军","疲惫的王庭军","年轻的女妖","特蕾西娅","菈玛莲","特雷西斯","阿斯卡纶"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_bg_49_g2_kazdelstreet_d.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_loneliness_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":8},{"type":"text","text":"卡兹戴尔地区，卡兹戴尔移动城市","id":9},{"type":"dialog","id":10},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4131_odda_1#2$1","duration":"0.5","id":11},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":12},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"让我过去！","id":13,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f4/Avg_avg_4131_odda_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":14},{"type":"charslot","id":15},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":16},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":17},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹王庭军","text":"前面已经封锁了，不能通行。","id":19,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_419_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":20},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4131_odda_1#2$1","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"那边发生什么事了？","id":22,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f4/Avg_avg_4131_odda_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":23},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","id":24},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹王庭军","text":"你是巴别塔的人？","id":26,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_419_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":27},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4131_odda_1#4$1","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"......我，我不是。","id":29,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a9/Avg_avg_4131_odda_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":30},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","id":31},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹王庭军","text":"那就与你无关。","id":33,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_419_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":34},{"type":"text","text":"奥达被挡在王庭军的人墙之外。","id":35},{"type":"text","text":"但在慌乱散开的人群中，他看到了几张熟悉的，正在哭泣的面孔。","id":36},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4131_odda_1#8$1","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"是那些学生......？这些房子......从小巷里绕一下，我应该能过去！","id":38,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/87/Avg_avg_4131_odda_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":39},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":40},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":41},{"type":"charslot","id":42},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","volume":"0","id":43},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.4","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"2","id":44},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":45},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":46},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4131_odda_1#2$1","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"可以告诉我那边到底发生什么事了吗？","id":48,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f4/Avg_avg_4131_odda_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":49},{"type":"charslot","id":50},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_932_1#1$1","duration":"1","bstart":"0.15","bend":"0.5","posfrom":"50,0","posto":"50,0","id":51},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_934_1#1$1","duration":"1","bstart":"0.15","bend":"0.5","posfrom":"-50,0","posto":"-50,0","id":52},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":53},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","focus":"l","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"冷漠的平民","text":"有人当街弄死了人，动手的人也死了。你要去凑热闹？","id":55,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_avg_npc_932_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激愤的平民","text":"又是巴别塔，也不知道殿下到底打算做什么......","id":57,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","focus":"l","id":58},{"type":"dialogue","name":"冷漠的平民","text":"......住嘴，尊重殿下！你吃的穿的住的不都是殿下为你带来的？！","id":59,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_avg_npc_932_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":60},{"type":"charslot","id":61},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","bstart":"0.15","bend":"0.5","duration":"1","id":62},{"type":"delay","time":"1.3","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"谨慎的平民","text":"嘘......","id":64,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":65},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4131_odda_1#2$1","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"......","id":67,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f4/Avg_avg_4131_odda_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":68},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_934_1#1$1","posfrom":"-50,0","posto":"-50,0","bstart":"0.15","bend":"0.5","id":69},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激愤的平民","text":"事情很简单——一个老师动手把自己学生的父亲给打死了！","id":70,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":71},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4131_odda_1#7$1","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"老师？怎么会......","id":73,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_4131_odda_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":74},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_934_1#1$1","posfrom":"-50,0","posto":"-50,0","bstart":"0.15","bend":"0.5","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激愤的平民","text":"那孩子的父亲不过骂了他两句！是那个老师自己说了些教坏小孩的话！","id":76,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":77},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4131_odda_1#8$1","id":78},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"不是这样的......","id":79,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/87/Avg_avg_4131_odda_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":80},{"type":"charslot","id":81},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_935_1#1$1","duration":"0.5","bstart":"0.15","bend":"0.5","id":82},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"讥讽的平民","text":"你也帮巴别塔说话？这样的年轻人他们都......","id":84,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_avg_npc_935_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":85},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4131_odda_1#9$1","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"......","id":87,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/24/Avg_avg_4131_odda_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":88},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_935_1#1$1","bstart":"0.15","bend":"0.5","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"讥讽的平民","text":"欸，你过去干什么？","id":90,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_avg_npc_935_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":91},{"type":"text","text":"奥达挤过了街道上的人群，他看到一些熟悉的面孔已经倒在地上。","id":92},{"type":"text","text":"当他好不容易来到混乱的源头时，他终于在扬起的尘埃中找到了那位“老师”。","id":93},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":94},{"type":"dialog","id":95},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"2","id":96},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":97},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4131_odda_1#2$1","id":98},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":99},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4131_odda_1#7$1","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"老师！到底是怎么回事？","id":101,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_4131_odda_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":102},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$dignified_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_dignified_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":103,"musicid":1},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“老师”","text":"我......真的没想......伤害......他爸爸......","id":105},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4131_odda_1#9$1","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"我带你去找医生！","id":107,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/24/Avg_avg_4131_odda_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“老师”","text":"不......那边......救他......","id":109},{"type":"text","text":"垂死的人指向了他一直望着的方向，奥达看到了一位受伤的孩子，守候在毫无动静的父亲身旁哭泣。","id":110},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4131_odda_1#9$1","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"......","id":112,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/24/Avg_avg_4131_odda_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":113},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":114},{"type":"charslot","id":115},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_bg_49_g2_kazdelstreet_d.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":116},{"type":"text","text":"奥达抱着受伤的孩子，穿越火光四起的街道时，终于从人群中拼凑出了一个真相。","id":117},{"type":"text","text":"一位激动的老师误杀了一位激动的父亲，随后被愤怒的人群包围，倒在了街道的尘埃里。","id":118},{"type":"text","text":"平民，巴别塔，佣兵，或许还有军事委员会，越来越多的人被卷入其中。","id":119},{"type":"text","text":"那里扬起的尘埃，从城市的一角，扩散到了城市的另一角......","id":120},{"type":"text","text":"直到巴别塔办事处的外墙被来源未知的炮火轰碎，王庭军才终于镇压下了这场引起轩然大波的混乱。","id":121},{"type":"text","text":"从一场意外开始，到一枚炮弹结束。巴别塔遭遇了自十八年前那场战争后，最大的损失。","id":122},{"type":"dialog","id":123},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":124},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_riot","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","volume":"0","id":125},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.4","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"2","id":126},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":127},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":128},{"type":"dialog","id":129},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4131_odda_1#5$1","duration":"0.5","id":130},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"不要逼我动手，这个孩子已经受伤了，需要医生。","id":132,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a3/Avg_avg_4131_odda_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":133},{"type":"charslot","id":134},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_053","duration":"1","id":135},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"沉默的佣兵","text":"你是哪边的？巴别塔？军事委员会？","id":137,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4131_odda_1#8$1","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"都不是，我只是想带他去找医生，请让开！","id":139,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/87/Avg_avg_4131_odda_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"虚弱的孩子","text":"我爸爸......","id":141},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4131_odda_1#9$1","id":142},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"来不及了......对不起。","id":143,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/24/Avg_avg_4131_odda_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_053","id":144},{"type":"dialogue","name":"沉默的佣兵","text":"......","id":145,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"沉默的佣兵","text":"走吧。但不要轻信外人......萨卡兹，现在局势很混乱。","id":146,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4131_odda_1#9$1","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"谢谢......","id":148,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/24/Avg_avg_4131_odda_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":149},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"2","id":150},{"type":"text","text":"奥达沉默地抱着孩子向前走去，孩子的呼吸逐渐衰微。","id":151},{"type":"text","text":"穿过街道时，奥达好像感觉到有人与他擦肩而过，但他却什么也没看到。","id":152},{"type":"dialog","id":153},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":154},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1304_1#1$1","afrom":"0.5","ato":"0.5","id":155},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":156},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":157},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":158},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":159},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":160},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4131_odda_1#4$1","id":161},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"......错觉吗？","id":163,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a9/Avg_avg_4131_odda_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":164},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":165},{"type":"charslot","id":166},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":167},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":168},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_496_1#1$1","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔成员","text":"站住！不要往前走了，里面还有病人。","id":170,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_496_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4131_odda_1#5$1","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"这个孩子需要救治，现在！","id":172,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a3/Avg_avg_4131_odda_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_496_1#1$1","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔成员","text":"可......现在这时候，你们还愿意把病人送来？","id":174,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_496_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔成员","text":"好吧，交给我。离开前，我会尽可能再给你们多留点药。","id":175,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_496_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4131_odda_1#8$1","id":176},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"离开？","id":177,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/87/Avg_avg_4131_odda_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_496_1#1$1","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔成员","text":"是殿下的决定。不过我们都清楚，其实是卡兹戴尔不再欢迎我们了。","id":179,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_496_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4131_odda_1#9$1","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"你们要到哪里去呢？城外？荒野上那么危险，你不害怕吗？","id":181,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/24/Avg_avg_4131_odda_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_496_1#1$1","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔成员","text":"......我害怕。","id":183,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_496_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔成员","text":"但如果这座城市不再接受我们，我们也尊重这座城市的决定。","id":184,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_496_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4131_odda_1#9$1","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"......","id":186,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/24/Avg_avg_4131_odda_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4131_odda_1#2$1","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"我想留在巴别塔帮些忙。照顾病人也好，帮你们维护安全也行。","id":188,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f4/Avg_avg_4131_odda_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":189},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":190},{"type":"charslot","id":191},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":192},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":193},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":194},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":195},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","focus":"l","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"冷淡的王庭军","text":"他就是引起骚乱的源头吗？他还能活吗？","id":197,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_419_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疲惫的王庭军","text":"失血过多，看上去救不回来了。","id":199,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_419_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","focus":"l","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"冷淡的王庭军","text":"那我们为什么还要守在这里？","id":201,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_419_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疲惫的王庭军","text":"按将军说的做，少问问题。谁能想到，一件小事最后闹到两位殿下不得不表态。","id":203,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_419_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“老师”","text":"呃......","id":205},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疲惫的王庭军","text":"他不会想和我们说话吧？这也没其他人啊？","id":207,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_419_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","focus":"l","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"冷淡的王庭军","text":"临死前的幻觉吧。像他这样的罪人，总不会有女妖来为他唱挽歌吧。","id":209,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_419_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":210},{"type":"charslot","duration":"0.5","id":211},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":212},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“老师”","text":"这里......危险......","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“老师”","text":"你......快走。","id":215},{"type":"dialog","id":216},{"type":"charslot","id":217},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1304_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":218},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":219},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年轻的女妖","text":"没事，他们看不透我的咒术，也抓不住我的身形。","id":220,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_avg_npc_1304_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":221},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“老师”","text":"你......是谁？","id":222},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1304_1#1$1","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年轻的女妖","text":"一个学生。","id":224,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_avg_npc_1304_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年轻的女妖","text":"沿着母亲的足迹自远方而来，我想在这座游荡的城市中寻求一些问题的答案，期待着两位殿下能够给我些许启迪。","id":225,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_avg_npc_1304_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":226},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“老师”","text":"你......找到......答案了吗？","id":227},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1304_1#1$1","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年轻的女妖","text":"我可能来得并不是时候，这座城市现在还无法给我答案。","id":229,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_avg_npc_1304_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年轻的女妖","text":"但是我发现了你。你宣扬的理想与主张，让我很感兴趣。","id":230,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_avg_npc_1304_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年轻的女妖","text":"当你躲在地下室里为那些孩子们授课的时候，我一直留在你们身边了解这座城市，了解巴别塔。","id":231,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_avg_npc_1304_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年轻的女妖","text":"当然，没人发现我......除了阿斯卡纶。","id":232,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_avg_npc_1304_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“老师”","text":"那个......孩子......","id":234},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1304_1#1$1","id":235},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年轻的女妖","text":"他被人保护着，送到巴别塔接受治疗了。","id":236,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_avg_npc_1304_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年轻的女妖","text":"关于你自己的结局，你后悔吗？","id":237,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_avg_npc_1304_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":238},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“老师”","text":"不......有孩子为我......辩护......","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“老师”","text":"有孩子......理解......我想改变的......东西......","id":240},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“老师”","text":"但......我对不起......我伤害了他的父亲——","id":241},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1304_1#1$1","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年轻的女妖","text":"我为你感到惋惜，这样的悲剧并非你本意，命运的愚弄偏偏降临在你身上。","id":243,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_avg_npc_1304_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“老师”","text":"我听到......哭声......","id":245},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1304_1#1$1","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年轻的女妖","text":"那是挽歌，它在彼岸呼唤你的逐渐黯淡的灵光。","id":247,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_avg_npc_1304_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年轻的女妖","text":"不必害怕，亦不必犹豫，众魂会接纳你，我的歌声会陪伴你前往彼岸。","id":248,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_avg_npc_1304_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":249},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“老师”","text":"谢谢......","id":250},{"type":"dialog","id":251},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"m","id":252},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":253},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":254},{"type":"text","text":"年轻女妖的歌喉抚平了即将死去之人的激荡思绪。","id":255},{"type":"text","text":"轻柔的吟唱萦绕在人潮汹涌的街道，引动着散落于城市各处的共鸣。女妖们回应着年轻女妖的哀曲，为其和音。","id":256},{"type":"text","text":"挽歌轻唱，纪念着一位平凡萨卡兹的离去。","id":257},{"type":"dialog","id":258},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":259},{"type":"text","text":"“在课堂上，你对巴别塔的未来没有讲完，后面是什么？”","id":260},{"type":"text","text":"“我认为......巴别塔注定会死去，但希望不会。”","id":261},{"type":"dialog","id":262},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":263},{"type":"charslot","id":264},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":265},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9b/Avg_bg_49_g5_furnaceplatform.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":266},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":267},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":268},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1071_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":269},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":270},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":271},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"歌声，又一位萨卡兹在这场混乱中逝去了......","id":273,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"这座城市不再有巴别塔的容身之处。我会带领他们离开这座城市。","id":274,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1071_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":275},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"不，特蕾西娅，我们都是爱戴您的......","id":276,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......我知道。但是巴别塔别无选择。","id":278,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1071_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"可您的离开......将会......","id":280,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我的人民已经做出了选择，我与特雷西斯都无法扭转他们的决定。","id":282,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我们还不能放弃希望。但现在，避免冲突是最好的选择。","id":283,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1071_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"......仇恨会如洪流般吞噬我们。","id":285,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1071_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":286},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"您早就知道......特蕾西娅，我们的英雄，我们的王。","id":287,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/81/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"温柔的祈求和温吞的变革，是说服不了因卡兹戴尔的崛起而被吸引至此的萨卡兹们的。","id":288,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/81/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":289},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......菈玛莲，我......","id":290,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1071_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":291},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"也许我会伤了您的心，特蕾西娅。","id":292,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/81/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"雷姆必拓，萨尔贡，甚至是哥伦比亚......您已经敲开了他们的门，让萨卡兹平等地和一些人......对视。","id":293,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/81/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"而又过了五十多年，泰拉大陆发生了过去几千年都未曾有过的技术变革，日新月异。","id":294,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/81/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":295},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......","id":296,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1071_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":297},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"......但我们的步伐还是太慢了。您给卡兹戴尔带来的这些匪夷所思的变化，仍只是变化，还没有开花结果。","id":298,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/55/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"哪怕，我也相信结果的春天已近在眼前。","id":299,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/55/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"这代表了女妖王庭现在的态度吗，菈玛莲？","id":301,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1071_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":302},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"这次我只是一个来送孩子远行的母亲，特蕾西娅。","id":303,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/81/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"我尊重他的想法，他也将代表王庭的态度。","id":304,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/81/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1071_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"但......不是现在。","id":306,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":307},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你很爱他，我能看出来......你将自己的时间凝固了。","id":308,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1071_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":309},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"哀珐尼尔是我的奇迹，也注定成为女妖们的奇迹。","id":310,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1071_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"自他出生的那一刻起，我就不愿随着岁月变迁而衰老。","id":312,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/81/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"这是我最为美丽的瞬间，我希望在他的记忆中......我亦是永恒。","id":313,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/81/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"当然，不变的只有外表，我的寿命终有一天会抵尽头。","id":314,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/81/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"......我的殿下。我知道您在想什么。","id":315,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/81/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"您本就觉得，这一代人无法完成您的宏愿，您本就觉得，您是土壤，不必见繁花盛开。","id":316,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/81/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"哪怕用您二位的一切来滋润这片土壤......","id":317,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/81/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":318},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......","id":319,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1071_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":320},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"满足我的小小私心吧，殿下。","id":321,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/81/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"此后的几年中，在他寻找到自己想要的答案前，他会来往于你们之间学习，接受你们的启迪。","id":322,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/81/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"他会成为钻出土壤的第一株顽强的幼苗。","id":323,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/81/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"请带上哀珐尼尔。请照顾好他。请替我保护他。","id":324,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/81/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":325},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我会的，菈玛莲。我的朋友。","id":326,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1071_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":327},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"谢谢。","id":328,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/76/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"无论将来的你们身处何处，无论你们之中谁将走向消亡，我与女妖的王庭都会共同为你们唱响挽歌，告知所有人......","id":329,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/76/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"这是我的许诺，是最古老强大的巫术，是我能为你们送出的最后离别之礼。","id":330,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/76/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":331},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"菈玛莲。","id":332,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"这会是我们最后一次见面吗？","id":333,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1071_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":334},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"我希望不是。","id":335,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":336},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"那么，再见吧，我还想在河谷的氤氲间听见你的轻唱。","id":337,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1071_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":338},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"再见，殿下。但是很抱歉，我只会留在这里，目送您远行。","id":339,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菈玛莲","text":"毕竟，哀珐尼尔将会加入你们的队伍，我......还不忍与他告别。","id":340,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_1071_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":341},{"type":"dialog","id":342},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":343},{"type":"charslot","id":344},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":345},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_bg_49_g6_babeloffice.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":346},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":347},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":348,"musicid":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":349},{"type":"text","text":"两天后","id":350},{"type":"dialog","id":351},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":352},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":353},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"......你还准备待多久？","id":354,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"如果你想等特蕾西娅，那你来得稍早了一些。","id":355,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":356},{"type":"charslot","id":357},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":358},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":359},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......","id":360,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":361},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"我以为你不敢来见我，阿斯卡纶。","id":362,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1","id":363},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"为什么？","id":364,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":365},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"是为什么你不敢来见我，还是为什么我要驱逐巴别塔？","id":366,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1","id":367},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......","id":368,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":369},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"你已经见过曼弗雷德了？","id":370,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1","id":371},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"是。","id":372,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":373},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"动手了？","id":374,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1","id":375},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"没动杀心。","id":376,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":377},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"也好。","id":378,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"在你开口说些幼稚的话前，离开吧。就算是特蕾西娅也不会同意你的想法。","id":379,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"当然，你也可以不解释任何事。留下。你从来没有正式加入过巴别塔。","id":380,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1","id":381},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"可殿下需要人保护。","id":382,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":383},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"她比你想的还要强大。","id":384,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1","id":385},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......而且我更加不认同你，老师。","id":386,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":387},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"......我会把这句话当做你的拒绝。","id":388,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1","id":389},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......","id":390,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":391},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"你和曼弗雷德都是我最得意的学生，你们都有自己致命的缺点。","id":392,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"你在战斗上的天赋出众，无人能及，但......你究竟有没有自己的信念？","id":393,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#4$1","id":394},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"殿下——","id":395,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3e/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":396},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"太急躁。","id":397,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"我说的是，“你自己的信念”。不是我的。不是特蕾西娅的。","id":398,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#8$1","id":399},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......","id":400,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b3/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":401},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"你至今还不明白自己在追求什么，不是吗？","id":402,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"保护？笼统而虚无的自我欺骗。你在迷茫之时只能将自己的动机投射到感性的情感之中。","id":403,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#3$1","id":404},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"我......想得很清楚。","id":405,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7a/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":406},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"......或许吧。","id":407,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"那就跟着特蕾西娅，保护好她。但也不要盲从于她，自己去想。曼弗雷德比你早很多得出答案。","id":408,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#3$1","id":409},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"下一次再见我的时候......","id":410,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":411},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"......不。","id":412,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"走吧。阿斯卡纶。","id":413,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"我们现在无话可说。","id":414,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":415},{"type":"text","text":"阿斯卡纶单膝向特雷西斯跪下，随后化作了雾气缭绕在特雷西斯的身边。","id":416},{"type":"text","text":"雾气颤动，继而消散，无影无踪，留下的，唯有特雷西斯手上的一柄石刃。","id":417},{"type":"text","text":"他想起了自己在天灾中抓住这个孩子的那一天。","id":418},{"type":"dialog","id":419},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":420},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","posfrom":"-100,0","posto":"0,0","id":421},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":422},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":423},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":424},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你对她太冷酷了，特雷西斯。","id":425,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"离别之时，你可以给她说说心里话，她不是一个擅长表达情感的孩子。","id":426,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":427},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"你比我更擅长教育她作为青年的那一面。","id":428,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":429},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你对她真的没有信心吗？","id":430,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":431},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"......我随时欢迎她回来。曼弗雷德在武艺上还是太懈怠，她会是个好师姐。","id":432,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":433},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我会转告她。","id":434,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":435},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"我更希望你也能回来。","id":436,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f7/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":437},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我知道。","id":438,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":439},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"如果这短暂的分裂都无法弥合，下次，我们面对的会是真正的内战。","id":440,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a2/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"那么，你我百余年的畅想，就皆是空谈。","id":441,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a2/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"到那时，如果不得不做，我会杀你。","id":442,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a2/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":443},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......","id":444,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/40/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":445},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"巴别塔也都准备好了，愿意跟随我们的人会一起出城。","id":446,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":447},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"......你总是带着他们。","id":448,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":449},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"是的，他们需要我。","id":450,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":451},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"可我也需要你，卡兹戴尔同样需要魔王。","id":452,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":453},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......特雷西斯。","id":454,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/73/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":455},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我们的子民已经做出了选择，至少现在，巴别塔的退让，是最好的选择。","id":456,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我会继续为卡兹戴尔唤来甘露，切实地改变这座城市的现状，等待恨意的平息。","id":457,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":458},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"但是......","id":459,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":460},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"如果在这个或许确实漫长的过程中，你成了那些尚且懵懂的理想者们最大的威胁，我也会毁灭你。","id":461,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/58/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":462},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"嗯。","id":463,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":464},{"type":"dialog","id":465},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":466},{"type":"charslot","id":467},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":468},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_bg_49_g2_kazdelstreet_d.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":469},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","volume":"0","id":470},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.4","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"2","id":471},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":472},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":473},{"type":"text","text":"成排的雇佣兵与王庭军伫立在街道的两侧维持着秩序，他们挡住了躁动不安的人们。","id":474},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"1.5","id":475},{"type":"dialog","id":476},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$storyendjp_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act5d0/m_avg_storyendjp_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":477,"musicid":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":478},{"type":"sticker","id":479,"text":"魔王带来足以果腹的食物与可以避寒的楼宇。","x":"320","y":"300","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"640","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":480,"text":"魔王无视人民遭受的压迫与积累的仇恨。","x":"320","y":"340","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"640","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":481,"duration":"1"},{"type":"sticker","id":482,"duration":"1"},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":483},{"type":"text","text":"一支望不到尾的巴别塔队伍背负着行囊默默前行，走过王庭军队列的人墙，走过了唾弃他们的人群身边。","id":484},{"type":"text","text":"特雷西斯走向人群，站在他们的身边。","id":485},{"type":"text","text":"近两百年来，他第一次离开了特蕾西娅的身侧。","id":486},{"type":"dialog","id":487},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":488},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":489},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我们都清楚自己将要面对什么。","id":490,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":491},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"希望这不会是你我最后一次并肩而立。","id":492,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","id":493},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......那一天还远吗？","id":494,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":495},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"不会太远。","id":496,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":497},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅走进了沉默的队列之中。与城市的告别是无声的，他们走在希望的道路上。","id":498},{"type":"text","text":"此刻，喧闹的声音黯淡下去，缓缓流动的队伍却有了片刻的停滞。","id":499},{"type":"text","text":"不再有谩骂，不再有哭泣，所有人都看到了——","id":500},{"type":"dialog","id":501},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":502},{"type":"charslot","id":503},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_49_i05.png","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.2","yScale":"1.2","id":504},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleFrom":"1.2","yScaleFrom":"1.2","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"60","id":505},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":506},{"type":"text","text":"维持秩序的佣兵跨出了队列，紧紧拥抱住人流中的挚友。","id":507},{"type":"text","text":"在巴别塔的废墟旁，他们在各自的耳畔说着什么，没人能听清，但所有人都愿意为他们的告别而驻足。","id":508},{"type":"text","text":"人民与人民的诀别，人民与城市的诀别。","id":509},{"type":"text","text":"那位已孤身一人的萨卡兹也行走在人流之中，没有遗憾。","id":510},{"type":"text","text":"他想起了那年自己跟着那位大哥哥出城寻找父母，他们也走在脚下这同一条道路上。","id":511},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"我相信，战争之外，一定还有一条路，爸爸。","id":512},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"我想，妈妈如此相信巴别塔，也是因为她渴望有不一样的生活。","id":513},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"再见了，爸爸，妈妈。","id":514},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"再见了，家乡。","id":515},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":516},{"type":"dialog","id":517},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":518},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":519},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_paper1","volume":"1","id":520},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":521},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅亲启，","id":522},{"type":"text","text":"我听闻了那座城市正在发生的事情，我对你的失落感同身受，卡兹戴尔于我们都有着特殊的意义。","id":523},{"type":"text","text":"但是巴别塔无需如无根之萍一般在荒野上流浪，我已经在雷姆必拓找到了我向你提起过的那艘舰船。","id":524},{"type":"text","text":"挖掘工作很顺利，两年的修复工作让这艘船已经恢复了基本的功能。","id":525},{"type":"text","text":"今后，它将载着巴别塔的希望继续航行。请等我回来，特蕾西娅。","id":526},{"type":"text","text":"另：我确实在这艘船内找到了它。","id":527},{"type":"text","text":"这是足以颠覆这个世界的遗产，而这是你们所生活的世界。","id":528},{"type":"text","text":"我想我有义务与你共同讨论。","id":529},{"type":"text","text":"——凯尔希","id":530},{"type":"dialog","id":531},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":532},{"type":"image","id":533},{"type":"charslot","id":534}],"characters":["奥达","萨卡兹王庭军","冷漠的平民","激愤的平民","谨慎的平民","讥讽的平民","“老师”","沉默的佣兵","虚弱的孩子","巴别塔成员","冷淡的王庭军","疲惫的王庭军","年轻的女妖","特蕾西娅","菈玛莲","特雷西斯","阿斯卡纶"]}